[p 
	[em 
		"Kirby's Dream Land 3
	]em
	" is the fifth platformer video game starring 
	[a href=/Game/group-kirby 
		"Kirby
	]a
	". Specifically, it is the third game under the Kirby's Dream Land name. Although the first two games were largely unrelated, Dream Land 3 features many returning characters from Dream Land 2. 
	[em 
		[a href=/Game/n64-kirby-64-the-crystal-shards 
			"Kirby 64: The Crystal Shards
		]a
	]em
	" was the sequel to this game. 
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"After the events of 
	[em 
		[a href=/Game/gb-kirbys-dream-land-2 
			"Kirby's Dream Land 2
		]a
	]em
	", Kirby and Gooey are on a fishing trip, when all of a sudden, Dark Matter appears and shatters the planet's rings. He then proceeds to possess various Dream-Landers, including King Dedede. Kirby and Gooey team up with Rick, Coo, and Kine, as well as new characters Pitch, ChuChu, and Nago, in order to stop Dark Matter.
	$LF
]p
